title: Grateful Dead Live at Civic Arena on 1988-06-26
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step, Little Red Rooster, When Push Comes To Shove, Mama Tried-> Big River, Cumberland Blues, Gentlemen Start Your Engines, Big Railroad Blues, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Touch Of Gray, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Playin' In The Band Reprise-> Drums-> Jam-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Hey Jude-> Black Peter-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Black Muddy River

reviews.review_text: Alvin! The pitch is way off on this.  Not really listenable.  Check UJB to SWIM.
